<div id="Layer1" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2"> <p align="left"><font class="atitulohistoria"><b> Joca quer ser</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeautores"><b> Ant&oacute;nio Torrado</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>escreveu</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeilustrador"> <b>Cristina Malaquias</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>ilustrou</b></font></p></td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20">&nbsp;</td><td width="50%"> <img align="right" border="0" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer2" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Perguntaram ao Joca o que &eacute; que ele queria ser quando fosse grande. S&atilde;o, &agrave;s vezes, muito <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[492],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">impertinentes</a> os senhores adultos.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Fez-se sil&ecirc;ncio na sala, &agrave; espera da resposta do menino.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Nisto, ouviu-se, na rua, uma ambul&acirc;ncia a apitar:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Ni-n&oacute;-ni... Ni-n&oacute;-ni...
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Logo o Joca respondeu:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Bombeiro.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer3" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Passado pouco tempo, outro senhor adulto fez a mesma pergunta ao Joca:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Quando fores crescido o que &eacute; que queres ser?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Entre a pergunta e a resposta um sil&ecirc;ncio, cortado pelo roncar, longe, de um avi&atilde;o:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Roooooooommm...
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Logo o Joca respondeu:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Aviador.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer4" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Minutos depois, mais um senhor curioso fez a pergunta do costume, precisamente na altura em que uma banda de rock pum-t&aacute;-tchim-pum se exibia na televis&atilde;o. O Joca respondeu:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	M&uacute;sico.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer5" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Mudaram de canal, por coincid&ecirc;ncia, quando o locutor gritava, a meio de um desafio de futebol:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Goooooolooooo!
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E o Joca tamb&eacute;m gritou:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Futebolista.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer6" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Nova mudan&ccedil;a de canal, para uma <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[493],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">correnteza</a> r&aacute;pida de not&iacute;cias, entre as quais um desfile militar, o que fez com que o Joca logo mudasse de opini&atilde;o e dissesse:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Soldado.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Na tribuna de honra, um respeit&aacute;vel senhor de cabelos brancos perfilava-se, diante das tropas em parada.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer7" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> O Joca n&atilde;o hesitou mais e disse:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Presidente da Rep&uacute;blica.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Bombeiro, aviador, m&uacute;sico, futebolista, soldado, Presidente da Rep&uacute;blica... Em que ficamos Joca?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Agora vou brincar - disse o Joca, cansado de ter passado por tantas profiss&otilde;es, em t&atilde;o pouco tempo.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer8" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Neco, o primo mais novo, seguiu-o a correr.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Ao que vamos brincar, Joca? - quis saber o Neco, que era muito bem mandado em coisas de brincadeira.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Vamos brincar aos bombeiros - decidiu o Joca.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Com ambul&acirc;ncias, carros encarnados, mangueiras?</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer9" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Vamos - entusiasmou-se o Neco.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Mas o Joca interrompeu-lhe os planos.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Vamos antes brincar aos aviadores - resolveu ele.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Com avi&otilde;es, aeroportos, para-quedas? Vamos - entusiasmou-se o Neco.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer10" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Nova interrup&ccedil;&atilde;o do Joca:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">-	Vamos antes brincar aos m&uacute;sicos.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E por a&iacute; fora, por a&iacute; fora, sem se decidir por uma brincadeira... Em que ficamos, Joca?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Se ele aqui estivesse e lhe apetecesse responder, talvez a resposta lhe sa&iacute;sse em verso, em forma de can&ccedil;&atilde;o ou pouco mais ou menos.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer11" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Cantiga do Joca
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Quero ser tudo
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">quero ver tudo
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">brincar a tudo
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">e mascarar-me,
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">fora do Entrudo,
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">de sobretudo,
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">feito <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[494],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">gra&uacute;do</a>
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">homem de estudo
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">muito sisudo
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">e carrancudo</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer12" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:405px; top:180px; width:315px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font class="historia-text"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">muito barbudo
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">e narigudo,
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">mas c&aacute; por dentro
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">nunca deixar
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">de ser mi&uacute;do.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%"></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="35%"><a href="imprimir.pdf" target="_blank"> <img src="../../../images/impre.jpg" align="left" border="0" width="20" height="20"></a><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow('../../../pop_votar.aspx?Mes=06&Dia=01','','menubar=no,width=270,height=170')"><img src="../../../images/votar_over.gif" align="right" border="0" width="67" height="20"></a></td></tr></table></div> 
